{
  "stem": "4963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in 1944-- of June 1944, the Russians marched back into Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- the-- the people-- the family announced that, you know, the Russians were there and that you're free now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I walked out, and again, approaching it as an adventure, and I went and I started going into the streets and, you know, meeting people and asking.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- you know, each-- many of the-- the ones who were hidden went out of hiding.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I am 14-- 14.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm just let out the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I-- you know, they-- they treated me nicely, these-- these people, and so they-- they-- in fact I think one of the daughters accompanied me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started meeting people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a Jewish community that was set up right away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a small city, so we really knew right away, you know, where the gathering place was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I went out there, I-- I met my uncle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in Kaunas.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was, I believe, on [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so the Jewish people started coming in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- this happened a few days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was over there, I went over there and went back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- and I met my Uncle Leiba, who was the doctor, my mother's-- my mother's brother, and his wife, who was a dentist, Hanna Taft, and their little boy, [?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mathis-- ?] no, it wasn't [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mathis. ?] It was Yasha, I believe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then two my-- two of my cousins, who were also their nieces and nephews, who also were in hiding in all different places.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we all survived, and they all gathered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my uncle was very well-known as a doctor in [INAUDIBLE], in that area, and he was very liked.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
